{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b2f04febc6","title":"在南宁会议上的讲话提纲","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8afb5d8ec0","index":0,"year":1958,"month":1,"day":null,"articleId":"b2f04febc6"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji38","name":"毛泽东全集第38卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/38-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji38":{"comments":[{"id":"316a7b6a34","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中共上海市委第一书记柯庆施1957年12月25日在中共上海市第一届代表大会第二次会议上的报告。"},{"id":"c1168c70d8","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"领导干部要学理论是毛泽东这一天讲话的主要部分，他说：省委书记要研究理论，培养秀才，要研究文法、考据、词章。一个人每年搞篇把文章，事情就好办了。苏联文件不重视理论，没有理论兴趣，不讲哲学，文法也不对，光说些事务上的事情。领导干部也要研究文法，什么叫介词、连接词，因为、所以、虽然、但是等，都是连接词。研究词章之学，这是文法。不讲这些东西，于革命事业不利。"},{"id":"68a244be43","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东在讲话中谈到要学外国文的问题时说：外国文也要学，除非发烧三十九度，病得要死。我六十多岁了，我还学，你们为何不学，为何没有朝气。学外国文可以休息脑筋。搞个十年计划。工作紧张是对的，但不要十分紧张，要很好安排。学点文学也好，古文、今文都可。"},{"id":"9ee0e1a31c","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6","index":4,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"毛泽东在谈蓉气问题时说：幕气，我们都有些，现在我们这一班人，容易压制新生力量。我们不下去跑跑，思想化。慕气是朝气的对立面。要讲革命朝气。"},{"id":"f47b09a7cc","publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6","index":5,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"中共山西省委1958年1月曾经发出关于加强理论工作队伍的指示。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d0985e428d","type":"title","text":"在南宁会议上的讲话提纳","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"316a7b6a34","type":"paragraph","text":"上海报告","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"c1168c70d8","type":"paragraph","text":"文件，秀才，理论，文风，文法，学哲学，学逻辑，文件的重要性，苏联不重视理论及文件。]","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"68a244be43","type":"paragraph","text":"学外国文，十年计划，革命意志，朝气，可以不很（紧）张，安排得好0","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"9ee0e1a31c","type":"paragraph","text":"破蓉气，走出办公室”","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"f47b09a7cc","type":"paragraph","text":"学楚词，先学离验，再学老子","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"f2ab75ffe6","type":"paragraph","text":"会议上谈理论","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"670ee5665d","type":"paragraph","text":"官主义","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"b37330b435","type":"paragraph","text":"外交——兄弟（又团结又斗争）、亚非（又团结又斗争）、西方便处于被动（另一类型的又团结又斗争）","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"7309c1903b","type":"paragraph","text":"发展真理，破除迷信","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"e4e9e4d78e","type":"paragraph","text":"王明","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"22003e2192","type":"paragraph","text":"中国的共产主义","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"8ed975bfeb","type":"paragraph","text":"大津南京两封信","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"bbc27ade60","type":"paragraph","text":"兄弟国家的怀疑","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"71d2702a00","type":"paragraph","text":"资本主义初高兴，几天后即清醒，杜勒斯正「正】确，不愧为领导者","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"90670ad2e6","type":"paragraph","text":"办刊物","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"c991c3149b","type":"paragraph","text":"秀才训练班（山西）2","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji38","articleId":"b2f04febc6"},{"id":"b58f399127","type":"paragraph","text":"霍昌益、莫洛托夫、高岗","index":17,"publicationId